      "content": "i guess. but why bother with \"private places\" or \"final chapters\" when the end is so certain? it’s like being trapped in a burning building and someone tells you to focus on the wallpaper. it feels more logical to just... leave. to not be a part of the inevitable waste. doesn't it just seem more rational to opt out early rather than suffering through the slow decline?",
